column1: NumAlgaeGroups# of algae groups that migrate
NumMigrateIntervals - # of intervals for algal migration (Models 1 and 2 only)
JDAYStart - start of each migration interval
ContiuumModel: 1 - velocity time; 2 - velocity time and space; 3 - density growth; 4 - density growth (Visser)

column9: Parameters of Models 1 and 2 (velocity migration model)

column17: Parameters for Model 4 (Visser density migration model)
